---
import SectionLabel from "@/components/SectionLabel.astro";
---

<section class="experience-preview page-shell" data-section-marker="Experience" data-section-tone="quiet">
  <SectionLabel label="Experience" labelEn="Experience" kicker="Career path" kickerEn="Career path" />
  <div class="experience-preview__grid">
    <p
      data-i18n-zh="我的工作重心从模型能力本身，逐渐转向模型如何进入真实业务系统：数据、权限、流程、评测和工程边界，往往比一次模型调用更决定产品质量。"
      data-i18n-en="My work has moved from model capability itself toward how models enter real business systems: data, permissions, process, evaluation, and engineering boundaries often decide product quality more than a single model call."
    >
      我的工作重心从模型能力本身，逐渐转向模型如何进入真实业务系统：数据、权限、流程、评测和工程边界，往往比一次模型调用更决定产品质量。
    </p>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div>
        <span>2026</span>
        <strong>Intelligent Bidding System</strong>
        <small>Document AI / RAG / Agent workflow</small>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span>2025</span>
        <strong>Enterprise OA Agent</strong>
        <small>Tool calling / approval / observability</small>
      </div>
      <div>
        <span>2024</span>
        <strong>AI Browser</strong>
        <small>Search / browser agent / VLLM</small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .experience-preview {
    padding-block: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
  }

  .experience-preview__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.8fr) minmax(0, 1.2fr);
    gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 6rem);
    margin-top: 1.8rem;
  }

  .experience-preview p {
    max-width: 35rem;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2.4vw, 2.1rem);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .timeline {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-line);
  }

  .timeline div {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 4.5rem minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 0.6rem 1.25rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    padding-block: 1.15rem;
  }

  .timeline span {
    grid-row: span 2;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
  }

  .timeline strong {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .timeline small {
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .experience-preview__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
